name: Rome Sun Lounger Armrest
description: For optimal outdoor durability, the frame is constructed in aluminium with an anthracite powder coated surface. The Rome outdoor fabric is a 100% PP material, specially developed to prevent water from penetrating, making it highly water and sunlight resistant. Add an oil-treated Australian Eucalyptus wood armrest to your sun lounger for complete flexibility and sunbathing comfort. The adjustable back allows you to read, relax, and nap in comfort.
